    "Reason : 1 - As a result of the excessive bulk, scale and depth of the first floor rear extension and its siting in relation to nos.30 and 34 Meadow Waye, the proposal would cause harm both to neighbouring living conditions and to the character and proportions of the original house. The proposal as a whole is therefore to conflict with Local Plan Policies CC1 (Context and Character), CC2 (Urban Design and Architecture) and SC7 (Residential Extensions and Alterations) and the intent of the Residential Extension Guidelines SPD."
